          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>In the <fr:link href="hmlg-000Q.xml" title="Abelian category" addr="hmlg-000Q" type="local">abelian category</fr:link> of modules over a ring <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex>, the <fr:link href="hmlg-0004.xml" title="Projective object" addr="hmlg-0004" type="local">projective object</fr:link> modules are exactly the modules that appear as a direct summand of some free module <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[P \oplus  Q = R^{\oplus  n}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
  
    
